}} 'Page' is a neighborhood in the Nokomis community in Minneapolis. Its
boundaries are the Minnehaha Creek to the north, Chicago Avenue to the east,
Diamond Lake Road and East 55th Street to the south, and Interstate 35W to the
west. Page shares a neighborhood organization with the Hale and Diamond Lake
neighborhoods.
